project_descr: The project is promoting the use of efficient electrical appliances and will be implemented under the UNEP Efficient Appliances Global Program Framework Document (PFD). The lead GEF agency will be UNDP.

outputs.output_descr: Assessment of the national energy efficiency and lighting regulatory and support mechanisms currently in place in Sudan, including the National Energy Efficiency Action plan (NEEAP)

project_title: leapfrogging sudan’s markets to effecient appliances
